@chapter GtkPreview
A widget to display RGB or grayscale data

@section Overview
The @code{<gtk-preview>} widget provides a simple interface used to display
images as RGB or grayscale data. It's deprecated; just use a @code{<gdk-pixbuf>}
displayed by a @code{<gtk-image>}, or perhaps a @code{<gtk-drawing-area>}.
@code{<gtk-preview>} has no advantage over those approaches.

